#. В§0: `(A : Prop)`
#. В§1: `(True : Prop)`
#. В§2: `(False : Prop)`
#: Game/Doc/Definition.lean:307
msgid "В§0 is any statement, without further specification as to whether it is true, false, or\n"
"unprovable.\n"
"\n"
"See also В§1 and В§2 for the unconditionally true and false\n"
"statements, respectively."
