msgid "В§0 (вҖңandвҖқ) is the statement that both В§1 and В§2 are true.\n"
"\n"
"## В§3 as a proof goal\n"
"\n"
"The tactic В§4 allows you to prove the two sub-statements В§5 and В§6 individually.\n"
"\n"
"## В§7 as an assumption\n"
"\n"
"With В§8, you break down an assumption of the form В§9\n"
"into its components В§10 and В§11."
msgstr ""

