#. ```
#: Game/Doc/Definition.lean:330
msgid "В§0 (вҖңorвҖқ) is the statement that at least one of the statements В§1, В§2 is true.\n"
"\n"
"## В§3 as proof goal\n"
"\n"
"You can use the tactics В§4 or В§5 to decide\n"
"which statement you want to prove.\n"
"\n"
"## В§6 as an assumption\n"
"\n"
"Since you do not know which of the statements В§7 or В§8 you can assume,\n"
"you may have to show the proof goal twice:\n"
"once under the assumption В§9 and once under the assumption В§10.\n"
"To do this, use the tactic\n"
"В§11"
msgstr ""

