#. В§11: `B`
#. В§12: `apply`
#: Game/Doc/Definition.lean:350
msgid "For В§0, В§1 is the implication вҖңВ§2 implies В§3.вҖқ\n"
"For other В§4, В§5 is a mapping that maps values from В§6 to В§7.\n"
"\n"
"## Implication as proof goal\n"
"\n"
"If your proof goal is an implication В§8, with В§9 you can assume В§10,\n"
"and then you must prove В§11.\n"
"\n"
"## Implication as assumption\n"
"\n"
"To use an implication among your assumptions, use the tactic В§12."
msgstr ""

