#. В§15: `mp`
#: Game/Doc/Definition.lean:365
msgid "В§0 means that statements В§1 and В§2 are logically equivalent (вҖңif and only ifвҖқ).\n"
"\n"
"## В§3 as proof target\n"
"\n"
"To show В§4, you can, for example, call В§5\n"
"and then prove В§6 and В§7 separately.\n"
"\n"
"## В§8 as an assumption\n"
"\n"
"You can break down an assumption of the form В§9 using В§10 into its two components\n"
"В§11 and В§12.\n"
"However, you can also refer directly to these components with В§13 and В§14.\n"
"(The abbreviation В§15 stands for вҖңmodus ponensвҖқ.)"
msgstr ""

