#. В§18: `a : A`
#. В§19: `ha : P a`
#: Game/Doc/Definition.lean:382
msgid "Existential quantifier: If В§0 is a predicate, then\n"
"В§1 is the statement that an element В§2 in В§3 (more precisely: of type В§4)\n"
"exists for which the statement В§5 is true.\n"
"A pure existence statement (\"there is an element of type В§6)\n"
"can be formulated, for example, as В§7 or as В§8.\n"
"\n"
"## В§9 as a proof goal\n"
"\n"
"To prove a statement of the form В§10,\n"
"you construct a suitable element В§11 and then use the В§12 tactic (В§13).\n"
"\n"
"## В§14 as an assumption\n"
"\n"
"You can decompose an assumption of the form В§15 into its components using\n"
"В§16 or В§17 into В§18 and В§19."
msgstr ""

